#Skill:  Last rites [9304]
#
Usage:  USE @@@@ <dead noble>
Time:   ten days

Attempt to commend a dead noble's body to its final resting place.
This prayer prevents the body from being resurrected or fouled in
any way.

Must be performed in a temple.  The dead noble's body need not
be present to execute this prayer.  Last rites has a 50% chance
of success.
